# === Rust ===
# Generated by Cargo — compiled files and executables
debug
target

# Backup files generated by rustfmt
**/*.rs.bk

# MSVC Windows builds of rustc generate these, which store debugging information
*.pdb

# Generated by cargo mutants
**/mutants.out*/

# === Node / tree-sitter ===
# Dependency installs
**/node_modules/

# Build artifacts (tree-sitter generate produces build/, *.so, *.dylib)
**/build/
*.so
*.dylib
*.a
*.o
*.pc

# npm lock file is left out of the tree-sitter subtree in the compiler repo
# convention — same here.
**/package-lock.json

# === Python / Pygments ===
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc
**/*.egg-info/
**/dist/
**/.pytest_cache/

# === VS Code extension packaging ===
*.vsix

# === IDE / editor local state ===
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*~

# === macOS ===
.DS_Store
